    "description": "Make our Indian twist on a bistro classic. You'll toss salad in a zingy dressing with roasted sweet potato and red onion, before topping with goats' cheese rolled in black sesame seeds. For a delicious kick, serve with fresh coriander chutney. All Health Hub recipes meet one of these criteria: <600 calories, 3 of your 5/day, or a source of protein.",
